actual.value: 2017:The Annual Supply Plan was prepared in the beginning of the year and regularly reviewed basis. This helped the office in identifying the yearly requirements leading to timely identification of new vendors, if needed, as well as establishment of the LTAs.

actual.value: 2014:22 LTAs as of 31 December 2014.Market survey conducted in the first quarter of the year and report submitted. Established 22 LTAs which has enhanced supply section effectiveness, competitiveness and value for money. The suppliers list updated on continuous basis.
